additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Starch (tapioca), prawn meat (4%), salt, sugar, flavour enhancer (E621), colours (E102, E124).

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: E102 & E124 May have an adverse effect on activity and attention in children.

additionalProperty.name: Country Of Origin
additionalProperty.value: Product of China from Imported ingredients

description: Double Phoenix Red Prawn Cracker is packed with light and crunchy crackers that are often found as an appetizer in Chinese restaurants or anywhere in Southeast Asia. Simply deep-fry them up in hot oil and they will puff up into a delicious finger food within seconds!
name: Red Prawn Crackers
